"title": "1140: God, the eternal",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1140",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God transcends all limitations of time and endures for ever.</p>\n<h2>God endures for ever</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:5\">NEH 9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:40\">DEU 32:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:26\">JOB 36:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:14\">PSA 48:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:12\">PSA 102:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>God transcends all concepts of time</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:8\">REV 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:4\">PSA 90:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:4\">ISA 41:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:8\">HEB 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:8\">2PE 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:17\">REV 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:13\">REV 22:13</a></p>\n<h3>He existed before time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:23\">PRO 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>He will exist after time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:11-Heb1:12\">HEB 1:11–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:26-Ps102:27\">PSA 102:26–102:27</a></p>\n<h2>The eternity of God's qualities</h2>\n<h3>His love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:34\">1CH 16:34</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:1\">PSA 106:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13\">2CH 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:17\">PSA 103:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:19\">HOS 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>His faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:5\">PSA 100:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps117:2\">PSA 117:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:6\">PSA 146:6</a></p>\n<h3>His power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:7\">PSA 66:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:11\">1PE 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>His righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:3\">PSA 111:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:3\">PSA 112:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:142\">PSA 119:142</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:24\">DAN 9:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's word is eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:31\">MRK 13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:24–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:8\">ISA 40:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's covenant is eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:7\">GEN 17:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:19\">NUM 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:10\">PSA 105:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:5\">ISA 24:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">ISA 55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:40\">JER 32:40</a></p>\n<h2>God's kingdom is eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:13\">PSA 145:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:18\">EXO 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7\">PSA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:19\">LAM 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:3\">DAN 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:14\">DAN 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's gifts are eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:29\">ROM 11:29</a></strong></p>\n<h3>He gives eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28\">JHN 10:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:47\">JHN 6:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7\">ROM 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></p>\n<h3>He gives eternal salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:17\">ISA 45:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:12\">HEB 9:12</a></p>\n<h3>He gives eternal joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:7\">ISA 61:7</a></p>\n<h3>He gives eternal possessions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:4\">GEN 48:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:8\">GEN 17:8</a></p>",
